content.title: RHBA-2019:0448: Red Hat OpenStack Platform 13.0 director Bug Fix Advisory (Moderate)
content.description:
Red Hat OpenStack Platform provides the facilities for building, deploying
and monitoring a private or public infrastructure-as-a-service (IaaS) cloud
running on commonly available physical hardware.

For more information about the bug fixes and enhancements included with this update, see the "Technical Notes" section of the Release Notes 
linked in the References section.
